\q1 “Balak summoned me to come here from Syria;
\q2 the king of Moab brought me here from the hills at the eastern side of Syria.
\q1 He said, ‘Come and curse the descendants of Jacob for me!
\q2 Come and say that bad things will happen to these Israeli people!’
